name: Palms n Sands Beach Restobar Candolim

reviews.review_text:
We had been to Palms n Sands for dinner. Half of the restaurant was under renovation. We got a table down by the beach which was amazing.

The food here is very delightful and yummy. We ordered Lamb Chops, Pork Chops and a few other chicken starters.
The good quality was up to the mark. The cocktails and the mocktails menu is very interesting and the drinks were great.

The only challenge we faced was with regards to the service and to be more specific the waiting time post the order.

Overall a good place to dine and would recommend to do reservations to get the best seats in the house.

A very good place to witness sunset. Good food and drinks with reasonable price. The place is quite elegant. Right on the candolim beach this has a silent and peaceful private kinda beach. Away from all noise the ambience is quite amazing.
Tables set up on sand.
The only problem is the service which is little slow. We had to wait for more than an hour for the food.

Amazing food, Amazing ambience
Perfect for family outing.
Kid friendly
A very good access to a very clean beach
It's a less crowded beach, great to have a nice relaxing time

description:
**Palms n Sands Beach Restobar: A Hidden Gem in Candolim, Goa**

Nestled right on the serene shores of Candolim Beach, Palms n Sands Beach Restobar boasts an impressive rating of 4.4 from nearly 5,000 enthusiastic diners. Notable for its picturesque sunsets—a frequent highlight with 102 mentions in reviews—the restaurant is frequently tagged for its charming shack-like ambiance and proximity to the iconic Fort Aguada. Signature dishes like crab au gratin have garnered plenty of praise, further solidifying its status as a must-visit culinary destination.

**Ambiance & Design**

Upon arriving at Palms n Sands, guests are immediately enveloped in a striking yet relaxed atmosphere. The establishment features elegant tables set upon the soft sand, providing an intimate dining experience with the gentle sounds of waves lapping at the shore. Despite recent renovations leaving part of the restaurant in transition, diners rave about the views, particularly during sunset, creating a romantic and picturesque backdrop for any meal. Reviewers have noted the peaceful vibe, making it feel like a private escape away from the hustle and bustle of Goa. From the captivating photos provided, one can appreciate the rustic décor accentuated with lush greenery and warm lighting that enhances the intimate feel of the beachside setting.

**Menu & Culinary Experience**

The culinary offerings at Palms n Sands are a delightful fusion of flavor and artistry. Diners have reported exceptional experiences with dishes including lamb chops and pork chops, complimented by a colorful array of cocktails and mocktails that change the game for refreshing drinks by the beach. The food presentation is as commendable as its taste, lavishly plated and arranged in a way that emphasizes the fresh, local ingredients. Many families have found the menu to be kid-friendly, ensuring that meals are enjoyable for all ages while maintaining high-quality standards and flavors.

**Customer Experience & Service**

While the culinary creations impress, feedback around service seems to feature some inconsistencies. Reviewers frequently recommend making a reservation, particularly if one desires a great table to view the sunset, though some patrons have noted challenges with waiting times. The service, while generally friendly and accommodating, can be a tad slower than anticipated; several guests mention waiting over an hour for their food. Nevertheless, the allure of the beach coupled with the delicious food offers a worthwhile trade-off for many.

**Popularity & Reviews**

The buzz around Palms n Sands is palpable. With nearly 5,000 reviews, a strong following extols its virtues across social media platforms, highlighting the unique mix of culinary experiences and stunning sunsets. Although there are remarks on the need for improved service speed, most reviews reflect a positive sentiment, often described as a great spot for family outings and romantic dinners alike. 

**Utilizing Visual Content**

With an impressive collection of customer images, one can get a glimpse into the vibrant energy of the restaurant. Pictures show diners enjoying lush dishes like crab au gratin and enjoying their time on the shoreline, reflecting the restaurant's appeal and lively atmosphere. The design of the space, particularly the tables set on the sand, further emphasizes its unique beachfront dining concept.

In conclusion, Palms n Sands Beach Restobar stands out as an inviting haven along the Goan coast, perfectly balancing delightful cuisine, breathtaking views, and a tranquil beach ambiance. For an experience that promises relaxation, good food, and the beauty of a sunset, it undoubtedly merits a visit.
